A Text Analysis of Dostoyevskys Books


By Genesis Data


I read Dostoyevskys books in the year of 1944, and I have no peace of mind since then


The aim of this project is to find certain words that give clues about the general framework of Dostoyevskys books. The project can show the most used words in the book, their sentiments, plot them, bigrams, etc.
